h","tag-manners-adab","tag-medicine-al-tibb","tag-pain-al-alam","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-visiting-the-sick-ad-marid"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-aJ5","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":771,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/10\/no-healing-but-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":41235,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Take away the pain by Your healing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would visit a sick person, he would say,\u00a0\u201cTake away the pain, O Lord of all people, and give healing for You are the Healer. There is no healing but Your healing, a healing that leaves no trace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19095,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/11\/angels-dua-visit-sick\/","url_meta":{"origin":41235,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Visiting: Angels bless one who visits a sick person","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever visits a sick person or visits his brother for the sake of Allah, a\u00a0heavenly\u00a0caller will announce: May\u00a0you\u00a0be blessed, may your walking be blessed, and\u00a0may you dwell in a residence of Paradise!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2008\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/11\/sickness-fire-expiate-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":41235,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fever: Sickness is fire from Allah to expiate sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, visited a man who was sick and he said, \u201cBe glad, for Allah has said: It is My fire that I afflict upon my sinful servant as his share in place of Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2088 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14254,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/18\/images-fabric-patterns\/","url_meta":{"origin":41235,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Images: Fabric with patterns, inscriptions on it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubaydullah ibn Abdullah reported: He entered the home of Abu Talhah when he was sick and he found Sahl ibn Hunayf with him. Abu Talhah called for someone to remove a sheet that was underneath him. Sahl said to him, \"Why did you remove it?\" Abu Talhah said, \"Because there\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21095,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\